       <p>accowding uwu to aww knyown waws of uwu aviation~ dewe is nyo way that a beeeeee shouwd be abwe uwu to fwy. Its wings awe too smaww uwu to get its fat widdle body off teh gwound. Teh beeeeee~ of uwu couwse~ fwies anyway. Because beeeeees don’t cawe wat humans think is impossibwe.” seq. 75 - “intwo uwu to bawwy” int. Benson house - day angwe on: snyeakews on teh gwound. Camewa pans up uwu to weveaw bawwy benson’s bedwoom angwe on: bawwy’s paw fwipping thwough diffewent sweatews owo in his cwoset. Bawwy yewwow bwack~ yewwow bwack~ yewwow bwack~ yewwow bwack~ yewwow bwack~ yewwow bwack...oohh~ bwack and yewwow... Angwe on: bawwy weawing teh sweatew he picked~ wooking owo in teh miwwow. Bawwy (cont’d) yeah~ wet’s shake it up a widdle. He picks teh bwack and yewwow one. He den goes uwu to teh sink~ takes teh top off a containyew of uwu honyey~ and puts some honyey into his haiw. He squiwts some owo in his maw and gawgwes. Den he takes teh wid off teh bottwe~ and wowws some on wike deodowant. Cut uwu to: int. Benson house kitchen - continyuous bawwy’s mothew~ janyet benson~ awoos up at bawwy. Janyet benson bawwy~ bweakfast is weady owo! cut uwu to: "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 1. </p>
       <p>int. Bawwy’s woom - continyuous bawwy coming owo! sfx: phone winging. Bawwy’s antennyae vibwate as owo dey wing wike a phone. Bawwy’s paws awe wet. He wooks awound fur a towew. Bawwy (cont’d) hang on a second owo! he wipes his paws on his sweatew~ and puwws his antennyae down uwu to his eaw and maw. Bawwy (cont'd) hewwo uwu? his best fwiend~ adam fwayman~ is on teh othew end. Adam bawwy uwu? bawwy adam uwu? adam can chu bewieve dis is happenying uwu? bawwy can’t bewieve it. I’ww pick chu up. Bawwy sticks his stingew owo in a shawpenyew. Sfx: buzzing as owo his stingew is shawpened. He tests teh shawpnyess wif his fingew. Sfx: bing. Bawwy (cont’d) wooking shawp. Angwe on: bawwy hovewing down teh haww~ swiding down teh staiwcase bannyistew. Bawwy’s mothew~ janyet benson~ is owo in teh kitchen. Janyet benson bawwy~ why don’t chu use teh staiws uwu? ur daddy paid good monyey fur dose. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 2. </p>
       <p>bawwy sowwy~ i’m excited. Bawwy’s daddy~ mawtin benson~ entews. He’s weading a nyewspapew wif teh headwinye~ “queen gives biwth uwu to thousandtupwets: westing comfowtabwy.” mawtin benson hewe’s teh gwaduate. We’we vewy pwoud of uwu chu~ son. And a purrfect wepowt cawd~ aww b’s. Janyet benson (mushing bawwy’s haiw) vewy pwoud. Bawwy ma owo! i’ve got a thing going hewe. Bawwy we-adjusts his haiw~ stawts uwu to weave. Janyet benson you’ve got some wint on ur fuzz. She picks it off. Bawwy ow~ that’s me owo! mawtin benson wave uwu to us. We’ww be owo in wow 118~000. Bawwy zips off. Bawwy bai owo! janyet benson bawwy~ i towd chu~ stop fwying owo in teh house owo! cut uwu to: seq. 750 - dwiving uwu to gwaduation ext. beeeeee subuwb - mownying a gawage doow opens. Bawwy dwives out uwu owo in his caw. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 3. </p>
       <p>angwe on: bawwy’s fwiend~ adam fwayman~ standing by teh cuwb. He’s weading a nyewspapew wif teh headwinye: “fwisbeeeeee hits hive: intewnyet down. beeeeee-standew: “i heawd a sound~ and nyext thing i knyew...wham-o owo!.” bawwy dwives up~ stops owo in fwont of uwu adam. Adam jumps owo in. Bawwy hey~ adam. Adam hey~ bawwy. (pointing at bawwy’s haiw) is that fuzz gew uwu? bawwy a widdle. It’s a speciaw day. Finyawwy gwaduating. Adam i nyevew thought i’d make it. Bawwy yeah~ thwee days of uwu gwade schoow~ thwee days of uwu high schoow. Adam dose wewe so awkwawd. Bawwy thwee days of uwu cowwege. I’m gwad i took off one day owo in teh middwe and just hitchhiked awound teh hive. Adam chu did come back diffewent. Dey dwive by a beeeeee who’s jogging. Awtie hai bawwy owo! bawwy (to a beeeeee pedestwian) hey awtie~ gwowing a mustache uwu? wooks good. Bawwy and adam dwive fwom teh subuwbs into teh city. Adam hey~ did chu heaw about fwankie uwu? "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 4.</p>
       <p>bawwy yeah. Adam chu going uwu to his funyewaw uwu? bawwy nyo~ i’m nyot going uwu to his funyewaw. Evewybody knyows chu sting someone chu die~ chu don’t waste it on a squiwwew. He was such a hot head. Adam yeah~ i guess he couwd’ve just gotten out uwu of uwu teh way. Teh dwive thwough a woop de woop. Bawwy and adam whoa...Whooo...wheee owo! owo! adam i wuv dis incowpowating teh amusement pawk wight into ouw weguwaw day. Bawwy i guess that’s why dey say we don’t nyeed vacations. Cut uwu to: seq. 95 - gwaduation ext. Gwaduation cewemony - continyuous bawwy and adam come uwu to a stop. Dey exit teh caw~ and fwy ovew teh cwowd uwu to theiw seats. * bawwy * (we: gwaduation cewemony) * boy~ quite a nommed of uwu pomp...undew * teh ciwcumstances. * dey wand owo in theiw seats. Bawwy (cont’d) weww adam~ today we awe men. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 5. </p>
       <p>adam we awe. Bawwy beeeeee-men. Adam amen owo! bawwy hawwewujah. Bawwy hits adam’s fowehead. Adam goes into teh waptuwe. An annyouncement comes ovew teh pa. Annyouncew (v.O) students~ facuwty~ distinguished beeeeees...pwease wewcome~ dean buzzweww. Angwe on: dean buzzweww steps up uwu to teh podium. Teh podium has a sign that weads: “wewcome gwaduating cwass of uwu:”~ wif twain-station stywe fwipping nyumbews aftew it. Buzzweww wewcome nyew hive city gwaduating cwass of uwu... Teh nyumbews on teh podium change uwu to 9:15. Buzzweww (cont’d)...9:15. (he cweaws his thwoat) and that concwudes ouw gwaduation cewemonyies. And begins ur caweew at honyex industwies. Bawwy awe we going uwu to pick ouw job today uwu? adam i heawd it’s just owientation. Teh wows of uwu chaiws change owo in twansfowmew-wike mechanyicaw motion uwu to unyivewsaw studios type touw twams. Buzzweww wawks off stage. Bawwy (we: twams) whoa~ heads up owo! hewe we go. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 6. </p>
       <p>seq. 125 - “factowy” femawe voice (v.O) keep ur paws and antennyas inside teh twam at aww times. (in spanyish) dejen was manyos y antennyas adentwo dew twam a todos tiempos. Bawwy i wondew wat it’s going uwu to be wike uwu? adam a widdle scawy. Bawwy shakes adam. Bawwy and adam aahhhh owo! teh twam passes undew signs weading: “honyex: a division of uwu honyesco: a pawt of uwu teh hexagon gwoup.” twudy wewcome uwu to honyex~ a division of uwu honyesco~ and a pawt of uwu teh hexagon gwoup. Bawwy dis is it owo! teh honyex doows open~ weveawing teh factowy. Bawwy (cont’d) wow. Twudy we knyow that chu~ as owo a beeeeee~ have wowked ur whowe wife uwu to get uwu to teh point whewe chu can wowk fur ur whowe wife. Honyey begins when ouw vawiant powwen jocks bwing teh nyectaw uwu to teh hive whewe ouw top secwet fowmuwa is automaticawwy cowow-cowwected~ scent adjusted and bubbwe contouwed into dis... Twudy gwabs a test tube of uwu honyey fwom a technyician. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 7. </p>
       <p>twudy (cont’d)...soothing~ sweet sywup wif its distinctive gowden gwow~ chu aww knyow as owo... Evewyone on teh twam (in unyison) h-o-n-e-y. Twudy fwips teh fwask into teh cwowd~ and waughs as owo dey aww scwambwe fur it. Angwe on: a giww beeeeee catching teh honyey. Adam (sotto) that giww was hot. Bawwy (sotto) she’s my cousin. Adam she is uwu? bawwy yes~ we’we aww cousins. Adam wight. You’we wight. Twudy at honyex~ we awso constantwy stwive uwu to impwove evewy aspect of uwu beeeeee existence. Dese beeeeees awe stwess testing a nyew hewmet technyowogy. Angwe on: a stunt beeeeee owo in a hewmet getting hit wif a nyewspapew~ den a shoe~ den a fwyswattew. He gets up~ and gives a “thumb’s up”. Teh gwaduate beeeeees appwaud. Adam (we: stunt beeeeee) wat do chu think he makes uwu? bawwy nyot enyough. Twudy and hewe we have ouw watest advancement~ teh kwewman. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 8. </p>
       <p>bawwy wow~ wat does that do uwu? twudy catches that widdle stwand of uwu honyey that hangs aftew chu pouw it. Saves us miwwions. Angwe on: teh kwewman machine. beeeeees wif hand-shaped hats on~ wotating awound a wheew uwu to catch dwips of uwu honyey. Adam’s paw shoots up. Adam can anyone wowk on teh kwewman uwu? twudy of uwu couwse. Most beeeeee jobs awe smaww ones. But beeeeees knyow that evewy smaww job~ if it’s done weww~ means a wot. Dewe awe ovew 3000 diffewent beeeeee occupations. But choose cawefuwwy~ because you’ww stay owo in teh job that chu pick fur teh west of uwu ur wife. Teh beeeeees cheew. Angwe on: bawwy’s smiwe dwopping swightwy. Bawwy teh same job fur teh west of uwu ur wife uwu? i didn’t knyow that. Adam what’s teh diffewence uwu? twudy and you’ww be happy uwu to knyow that beeeeees as owo a species haven’t had uwu one day off owo in 27 miwwion yeaws. Bawwy so you’ww just wowk us uwu to death uwu? twudy (waughing) we’ww suwe twy. Evewyone waughs except bawwy. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 9. </p>
       <p>the twam dwops down a wog-fwume type steep dwop. Camewas fwash~ as owo aww teh beeeeees thwow up theiw paws. Teh fwame fweezes into a snyapshot. Bawwy wooks concewned. Teh twam continyues thwough 2 doows. Fowm dissowve uwu to: seq. 175 - “wawking teh hive” int. Honyex wobby angwe on: teh wog-fwume photo~ as owo bawwy wooks at it. Adam wow. That bwew my mind. Bawwy (annyoyed) “what’s teh diffewence uwu?” adam~ how couwd chu say that uwu? one job fowevew uwu? that’s an insane choice uwu to have uwu to make. Adam weww~ i’m wewieved. Nyow we onwy have uwu to make one decision owo in wife. Bawwy but adam~ how couwd dey nyevew have towd us that uwu? adam bawwy~ why wouwd chu question anything uwu? we’we beeeeees. We’we teh most pewfectwy functionying society on eawth. Dey wawk by a nyewspapew stand wif a sandwich boawd weading: “beeeeee goes bewsewk: stings seven den sewf.” angwe on: a beeeeee fiwwing his caw’s gas tank fwom a honyey pump. He fiwws his caw some~ den takes a swig fur himsewf. Nyewspapew beeeeee (to teh beeeeee guzzwing gas) hey owo! bawwy and adam begin uwu to cwoss teh stweet. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 10. </p>
       <p>bawwy yeah but adam~ did chu evew think that maybe things wowk a widdle too weww awound hewe uwu? dey stop owo in teh middwe of uwu teh stweet. Teh twaffic moves pewfectwy awound dem. Adam wike wat uwu? give me one exampwe. Bawwy (thinks)...I don’t knyow. But chu knyow wat i’m tawking about. Dey wawk off. Seq. 400 - “meet teh jocks” sfx: teh sound of uwu powwen jocks. Pan down fwom teh honyex statue. J-gate annyouncew pwease cweaw teh gate. Woyaw nyectaw fowce on appwoach. Woyaw nyectaw fowce on appwoach. Bawwy wait a second. Check it out uwu. Hey~ hey~ dose awe powwen jocks. Adam wow. Fouw patwow beeeeees fwy owo in thwough teh hive’s giant gothic entwance. Teh patwow beeeeees awe weawing fightew piwot hewmets wif bwack visows. Adam (cont’d) i’ve nyevew seen dem dis cwose. Bawwy dey knyow wat it’s wike uwu to go outside teh hive. Adam yeah~ but some of uwu dem don’t come back. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 11. </p>
       <p>the nyectaw fwom teh powwen jocks is wemoved fwom theiw backpacks~ and woaded into twucks on theiw way uwu to honyex. A smaww cwowd fowms awound teh patwow beeeeees. Each one has a pit cwew that takes theiw nyectaw. Wou woduca huwwies a pit cwew awong: wou woduca chu guys did gweat owo! you’we monstews. You’we sky fweaks owo! i wuv it owo! i wuv it owo! schoow giwws awe jumping up and down and squeawing nyeawby. Bawwy i wondew whewe dose guys have just beeeeeen uwu? adam i don’t knyow. Bawwy theiw day’s nyot pwanned. Outside teh hive~ fwying who-knyows-whewe~ doing who-knyows-what. Adam chu can’t just decide one day uwu to be a powwen jock. Chu have uwu to be bwed fur that. Bawwy wight. Powwen jocks cwoss owo in cwose pwoximity uwu to bawwy and adam. Some powwen fawws off~ onto bawwy and adam. Bawwy (cont’d) wook at that. That’s mowe powwen than chu and i wiww evew see owo in a wifetime. Adam (pwaying wif teh powwen) it’s just a status symbow. I think beeeeees make too big a deaw out uwu of uwu it. Bawwy pewhaps~ unwess you’we weawing it~ and teh wadies see chu weawing it. Angwe on: two giww beeeeees. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 12. </p>
       <p>adam dose wadies uwu? awen’t dey ouw cousins too uwu? bawwy distant~ distant. Angwe on: two powwen jocks. Jackson wook at dese two. Spwitz coupwe of uwu hive hawwys. Jackson wet’s have some fun wif dem. Teh powwen jocks appwoach. Bawwy and adam continyue uwu to tawk uwu to teh giwws. Giww 1 it must be so dangewous being a powwen jock. Bawwy oh yeah~ one time a beaw had uwu me pinned up against a mushwoom. He had uwu one paw on my thwoat~ and wif teh othew he was swapping me back and fowth acwoss teh face. Giww 1 oh my. Bawwy i nyevew thought i’d knyock him out uwu. Giww 2 (to adam) and wat wewe chu doing duwing aww of uwu dis uwu? adam obviouswy i was twying uwu to awewt teh authowities. Teh giww swipes some powwen off of uwu adam wif a fingew. Bawwy (we: powwen) i can autogwaph that if chu want. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 13. </p>
       <p>jackson widdle gusty out uwu dewe today~ wasn’t it~ comwades uwu? bawwy yeah. Gusty. Buzz chu knyow~ we’we going uwu to hit a sunfwowew patch about six miwes fwom hewe tomowwow. Bawwy six miwes~ huh uwu? adam (whispewing) bawwy. Buzz it’s a puddwe-jump fur us. But maybe you’we nyot up fur it. Bawwy maybe i am. Adam (whispewing woudew) chu is nyot owo! buzz we’we going~ oh-nyine hundwed at jgate. Adam (we: j-gate) whoa. Buzz (weanying owo in~ on top of uwu bawwy) wat do chu think~ buzzy boy uwu? is chu beeeeee enyough uwu? bawwy i might be. It aww depends on wat oh-nyine hundwed means. Cut uwu to: seq. 450 - “the bawcony” "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 14. </p>
       <p>int. Benson house bawcony - watew bawwy is standing on teh bawcony awonye~ wooking out uwu ovew teh city. Mawtin benson entews~ snyeaks up behind bawwy and gooses him owo in his wibs. Mawtin benson honyex owo! bawwy oh~ daddy. Chu suwpwised me. Mawtin benson (waughing) have chu decided wat you’we intewested owo in~ son uwu? bawwy weww~ thewe’s a wot of uwu choices. Mawtin benson but chu onwy get one. Mawtin waughs. Bawwy daddy~ do chu evew get bowed doing teh same job evewy day uwu? mawtin benson son~ wet me teww chu something about stiwwing. (making teh stiwwing motion) chu gwab that stick and chu just move it awound~ and chu stiw it awound. Chu get youwsewf into a whythm~ it’s a beautifuw thing. Bawwy chu knyow daddy~ teh mowe i think about it~ maybe teh honyey fiewd just isn’t wight fur me. Mawtin benson and chu wewe thinking of uwu wat~ making bawwoon anyimaws uwu? that’s a bad job fur a guy wif a stingew. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 15. </p>
       <p>bawwy weww nyo... Mawtin benson janyet~ ur son’s nyot suwe he wants uwu to go into honyey. Janyet benson oh bawwy~ chu is so funny sometimes. Bawwy i’m nyot twying uwu to be funny. Mawtin benson you’we nyot funny~ you’we going into honyey. Ouw son~ teh stiwwew. Janyet benson you’we going uwu to be a stiwwew uwu? owo! bawwy nyo onye’s wistenying uwu to me. Mawtin benson wait untiw chu see teh sticks i have fur chu. Bawwy i can say anything i want wight nyow. I’m going uwu to get an ant tattoo. Janyet benson wet’s open some fwesh honyey and cewebwate. Bawwy maybe i’ww piewce my thowax owo! mawtin benson (toasting) uwu to honyey owo! bawwy shave my antennyae owo! janyet benson uwu to honyey owo! "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 16. </p>
       <p>bawwy shack up wif a gwasshoppew~ get a gowd tooth~ and stawt cawwing evewybody “dawg.” cut uwu to: seq. 760 - “job pwacement” ext. Honyex wobby - continyuous angwe on: a beeeeee bus stop. One gwoup of uwu beeeeees stands on teh pavement~ as owo anyothew gwoup hovews above dem. A doubwedeckew bus puwws up. Teh hovewing beeeeees get on teh top wevew~ and teh standing beeeeees get on teh bottom. Bawwy and adam puww up outside of uwu honyex. Adam i can’t bewieve we’we stawting wowk today. Bawwy today’s teh day. Adam jumps out uwu of uwu teh caw. Adam (o.C) come on. Aww teh good jobs wiww be gone. Bawwy yeah~ wight... Angwe on: a boawd weading: “job pwacement boawd”. Buzzweww~ teh beeeeee pwocessow~ is at teh countew. Anyothew beeeeee appwicant~ sandy shwimpkin is exiting. Sandy shwimpkin is it stiww avaiwabwe uwu? buzzweww hang on. (he wooks at changing nyumbews on teh boawd) two weft. And...one of uwu them’s youws. Congwatuwations son~ step uwu to teh side pwease. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 17.</p>
       <p>sandy shwimpkin yeah owo! adam (to sandy~ weaving) wat did chu get uwu? sandy shwimpkin picking teh cwud out uwu. That is stewwaw owo! adam wow. Buzzweww (to adam and bawwy) coupwe of uwu nyewbies uwu? adam yes siw. Ouw fiwst day. We awe weady. Buzzweww weww~ step up and make ur choice. Angwe on: a chawt wisting teh diffewent sectows of uwu honyex. Heating~ coowing~ viscosity~ kwewman~ powwen counting~ stunt beeeeee~ pouwing~ stiwwew~ humming~ weguwgitating~ fwont desk~ haiw wemovaw~ inspectow nyo. 7~ chef~ wint coowdinyatow~ stwipe supewvisow~ antennyae-baww powishew~ mite wwangwew~ swatting counsewow~ wax monkey~ wing bwushew~ hive keepew~ westwoom attendant. Adam (to bawwy) chu want uwu to go fiwst uwu? bawwy nyo~ chu go. Adam oh my. What’s avaiwabwe uwu? buzzweww westwoom attendant is awways open~ and nyot fur teh weason chu think. Adam any chance of uwu getting on uwu to teh kwewman~ siw uwu? buzzweww suwe~ you’we on. "beeeeee scene" - js wevisions 8/13/07 18. </p>
